A vintage-style technical blueprint illustration showing an intricate web of interconnected document nodes floating in space, each node depicted as a layered paper document with multiple tabs and folded corners, connected by flowing copper-colored data streams and ornate mechanical gears. The documents are arranged in a non-hierarchical organic pattern resembling a neural network, with some nodes larger than others, casting soft shadows on an aged cream-colored parchment background. Sepia tones dominate with accents of deep burgundy and antique brass, featuring delicate hand-drawn crosshatching and technical drafting lines reminiscent of 19th-century engineering drawings.
